1. *Grešiš* ako misliš da ćeš to uspeti sam. (You are mistaken if you think you can do it alone.)
2. On *greši* u svom zaključivanju. (He makes mistakes in his reasoning.)
3. Nemojte mi zameriti ako *grešim*, ali mislim da ste pogrešili. (Please don't be angry with me if I am wrong, but I think you made a mistake.)
4. *Grešili* su mnogi pre vas, ali to ne znači da i vi morate. (Many have made mistakes before you, but that doesn't mean you have to as well.)
5. Ako *ne grešim*, taj film je izašao pre dva meseca. (If I'm not mistaken, that movie came out two months ago.)
6. *Greška* koju sam napravio bila je presudna. (The mistake I made was crucial.)
7. Koliko god da *grešiš*, nikada ne smiješ odustati. (No matter how much you fail, you should never give up.)